### NFSIM-EDA-01 — EDA Wrist Sensor

**README.** Electrodermal activity (skin conductance) wrist sensor. Stress, emotional state, sympathetic nervous system activation.

**SPECIFICATIONS.** ADS1256 + 500 mV AC bridge for skin conductance; 1 µS resolution; BLE; 24h battery; ~$42.

**THEORY.** Skin conductance rises with sweat gland activation (sympathetic). AC excitation avoids electrode polarization.

**ASSEMBLY.** Wristband with two skin-contact electrodes on inside of wrist.
